claim.claim-text:
A method (200) comprising:
obtaining at least one image of media as the media is being transported through a dispenser (step 210);
extracting one or more of: a denomination for the media and a serial number for the media from the at least one image prior to dispensing the media (step 220);
sending the extracted information to a controller (step 230), and
diverting the media to a reject compartment in the event that the controller indicates that the extracted information satisfies a rejection criterion.
